snippet.title: How To Hack In - the beginning (hacking simulation game announcement)
snippet.description:
The new hacking game simulation in progress - are you ready to become a hacker? The game will offer freedom in story progression, as well as in choosing the way to break into the systems.
More detailed info shortly, subscribe to be always informed!
